name: Bon fire
description: A roaring bonfire casts a warm, golden glow against the encroaching twilight. Sparks dance upward, merging with the darkening sky, while shadows flicker on the faces of onlookers huddled around. The crackling wood sends occasional bursts of light, creating a cozy, inviting ambiance that contrasts with the cool, crisp night air.
